sequenceDiagram
  participant Payments as demo-app payments
  participant Prom as Prometheus
  participant AM as Alertmanager
  participant API as causa-api
  participant Triage as Triage MCP client
  participant Grafana as Grafana MCP
  participant GitHub as GitHub MCP
  participant Topo as TopologySource
  participant Inv as Investigator
  participant Agent as Cursor Cloud Agent
  participant Console as causa-console

  Payments->>Prom: OTLP metrics (p99, pool in-use)
  Prom->>AM: PaymentsHighLatencyP99 firing
  AM->>API: POST /webhook/alert
  API->>Triage: assemble_brief()
  Triage->>Grafana: query_prometheus, generate_deeplink
  Triage->>GitHub: list merged PRs in window
  Grafana-->>Triage: metric signatures
  GitHub-->>Triage: candidate changes
  API->>Topo: dependents(payments)
  Topo-->>API: blast radius services
  API->>Inv: investigate(brief)
  Inv->>Agent: clone repo, trace, test
  Agent-->>Inv: JSONL event stream
  Agent-->>API: RCA JSON
  API->>API: validate against contract
  API-->>Console: investigation + RCA + deeplinks
